node.text: What a lovely thing to do! I don’t have pebbles this pretty around  where I live!!🥰

Painted pebbles… 🎨🖌️

I gave the pebbles a coat of matt white spray paint first as a plain base to work on. I then used acrylic paints for the bold shapes, using masking tape for any straight lines… and a black fine liner for the drawings ☺️
What a lovely thing to do! I don’t have pebbles this pretty around  where I live!!🥰
Your creativity is such a joy to behold! 💖
so beautiful! I collected some perfect rocks on our recent roadtrip in Australia and was thinking of painting them and giving them away... thank you for sharing your process 🙏🙏🙏

caption.text:
Painted pebbles… 🎨🖌️

I gave the pebbles a coat of matt white spray paint first as a plain base to work on. I then used acrylic paints for the bold shapes, using masking tape for any straight lines… and a black fine liner for the drawings ☺️
